title: World of tanks mods by HAVOC
description:
This is a collection of mods for world of tanks patch 8.10
including:

Gun sights, not Jimbo's
Sniper zoom, 30x
Over tank marker
Locastan's minimap
advanced mini map showing turret direction of enemy tanks
Accurate damage indicator
Maximum view removes foggy haze from maps
Romkyn's 3D icons for tanks
Received damage notifier gives you what kind of shell hit your tank and from who
Painted targets, paints each tank of where to aim at.
